      <odd id="aspace_ee0085f6d3a81401299bf3721e3e4e77">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 38-B (YRG 38-B), Records documenting specific sports at Yale.</p>  
      </odd>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_6f619d49f8129278910e232f958a08b0">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The records were transferred from the Department of Athletics, 2005; gift of the Connecticut Historical Society, 2012.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_68089e8c21919b9b0f7ec55819af07cd">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>Access to the materials is partially restricted. See inventory for details. Scrapbooks from 1918-1969 have been microfilmed. Patrons must use HM 178 instead of the originals.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <userestrict id="aspace_89bfabb4da67b12e1fb09b362e695dd5">
         <head>Conditions Governing Use</head>
         <p>Patrons must use HM FILM 178 instead of the original scrapbooks for the years 1918-1969.</p>  
      </userestrict>
      <prefercite id="aspace_2486a4fd8629cb77ad48e4681347a1e4">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Department of Athletics, Yale University, Records Documenting Tennis (RU 942). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <arrangement id="aspace_aeb32b0ba08d53ff09d50faf8d72f1af">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged by accession.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_7dfdc5119b462790751d188e9eabb4e9">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of scrapbooks, correspondence, memos, and reports documenting tennis at Yale.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
